Package hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis.algorithm.bmc

Class BmcTrace<S extends ExprState,A extends StmtAction>

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis.algorithm.bmc.BmcTrace<S,A>
public final class BmcTrace<S extends ExprState,A extends StmtAction> extends Object
Represents a mutable, alternating trace in the form of a (State, Action, State, ..., State, Action, State) sequence. A trace always contains at least one state and the number of actions is one less than the number of states.
